<B>__{an empty stall.}
<A>__{the automatic toilet flushes itself. the man takes a half step in, confused. suddenly charlie's angels 8 18 99 the door swings back, smashing into his right hand. he drops the gun, looking up to see natalie, who is perched atop the stall walls. she pushed the door with her foot. grabbing an overhead pipe, she performs an acrobatic swing, landing both feet on the guy's head. he falls into the next row of stalls. natalie reaches for the gun, but the man grabs her ankles. he pulls her back across the tile floor, flipping her over. that just makes it easier for her to kick him where it counts. with a scissors lock around his neck, natalie is pulled up while the man falls. she lands a knee on his windpipe.}
